{"tid":793452,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有線獨家直播超過100場「歐洲國家聯賽」","createTime":"2018-08-25T12:33:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T19:46:55.000Z","uid":37528,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e857b70f5a8c72be46a4ad957f9a9241a8633a5c","tid":793452,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T12:33:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">是咁的</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，有線喺尋日（禮拜五）喺facebook開咗個post，公佈將會獨家直播超過100場「歐洲國家聯賽」！喂，「歐洲國家聯賽」喎，咁咪即時英超、意甲、西甲同埋徳甲都有！哈哈，咁多位fans，<span style=\"color: red;\">你太年輕了！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n皆因有線個facebook post之後有解釋話：「歐洲國家聯賽 (UEFA Nations League)是歐洲國家隊足球賽事，今年為首屆賽事並於2018年9月6日至2019年6月9日舉行...」時間關係，下刪幾十字，簡單啲講，即係<span style=\"color: red;\">「唔是」</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 英超、意甲、西甲同埋徳甲啦。喺呢個moment，<span style=\"color: red;\">又到咗識睇，一定係睇留言嘅時間</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，又係時間關係，揀幾段精采啲嘅留言畀大家睇：<br />\n<br />\n網民1號：越做越差，連德甲都放棄埋，好波！<br />\n網民2號：我支持咗有線直播德甲差唔多20年，希望有線千萬不要放棄德甲！放棄德甲等如放棄生存<br />\n網民3號：仲以為有德甲睇，原來...真係火都嚟！<br />\n網民4號：德甲都唔播，歐聯又話唔知，又唔退月費<br />\n網民5號：買埋啲雞肋，唔買德甲歐聯，咩原因？難道歐洲國家聯賽個個禮拜有得睇？<br />\n<br />\n不過網民咁嬲係有原因嘅，皆因大家都想聽到劉舜文講德甲嘛！綽號「有線歌王」嘅佢都係facebook開post話：「近日有大量球迷喺fb留言或inbox message 詢問有關德甲轉播權的問題，我亦明白德甲星期五就正式開鑼。之但係，請原諒小弟只係一位評述員/體育主持，我所知嘅嘢，或收到嘅消息，其實唔會比大家多好多、快好多同準好多。」佢又話好衷心感謝各位對自己嘅支持，同埋對德甲嘅著緊！<br />\n<br />\n蘋果篇野邊個寫，好撚on9同小學雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw，有線真係不如執左佢把啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60a0962091f22f290399c9d18dd7b9d94b983ece","tid":793452,"uid":1880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T12:44:23.000Z","msg":"體育版中學畢業都做得，係咁上下啦"},{"pid":"a7c9a3ce43442c24b19303b5ef3e91623f3128b3","tid":793452,"uid":22948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T18:18:04.000Z","msg":"發夢夢見好似馬會買歐聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05cc8df5cdb41ff18e38cd5acbbdef6cdf55ba76","tid":793452,"uid":54025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7c9a3ce43442c24b19303b5ef3e91623f3128b3","tid":793452,"uid":22948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T18:18:04.000Z","msg":"發夢夢見好似馬會買歐聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T18:19:58.000Z","msg":"好似依家都未傾惦有線有無得播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"304887a2b8d8e7c56218087e4e1830ca66065c69","tid":793452,"uid":47485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7c9a3ce43442c24b19303b5ef3e91623f3128b3","tid":793452,"uid":22948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T18:18:04.000Z","msg":"發夢夢見好似馬會買歐聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T18:53:20.000Z","msg":"即係點<br />\n馬會開通宵俾班阿叔睇波？"},{"pid":"ebac2838d46bc324b8d02f8d176926d2588769cf","tid":793452,"uid":46151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"304887a2b8d8e7c56218087e4e1830ca66065c69","tid":793452,"uid":47485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7c9a3ce43442c24b19303b5ef3e91623f3128b3","tid":793452,"uid":22948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T18:18:04.000Z","msg":"發夢夢見好似馬會買歐聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T18:53:20.000Z","msg":"即係點<br />\n馬會開通宵俾班阿叔睇波？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T19:00:52.000Z","msg":"馬會自己有個hkjctv"},{"pid":"8f8c68471e25e4d4d1f35efaa9b06a1f8b16795d","tid":793452,"uid":47485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ebac2838d46bc324b8d02f8d176926d2588769cf","ti